1. *Majko* mi je rekla da budem strpljiv. (My mother told me to be patient.)
2. *Majko* moja, je li to istina? (My mother, is that true?)
3. Ova slika je moja *majka*. (This picture is my mother.)
4. *Majku* mi nikada neću zaboraviti. (I will never forget my mother.)
5. Nije poštovao svoju *majku*. (He didn't respect his mother.)